from new business wins and a recovering market.
At an operating segment level, Pest Elimination fixed currency sales increased 11% in 2022 reflecting strong growth
across food retail, food & beverage, hospitality and restaurants from accelerating pricing and new business wins .
Fixed currency sales increased 11% in 2021 reflecting strong growth in food and beverage plants, restaurants and
hospitality markets. Textile Care fixed currency sales increased 19% and 10% in 2022 and 2021, respectively.
