The difference in the weighted average common shares outstanding for calculating basic and diluted earnings
attributable to Ecolab per common share is a result of the dilution associated with the Company’s equity compensation
plans. As noted in the table below, certain stock options and units outstanding under these equity compensation plans
were not included in the computation of diluted earnings attributable to Ecolab per common share because they would
not have had a dilutive effect.
