expects to incur pre-tax charges of $195 million ($150 million after tax). The Company expects that these restructuring
actions will be completed by 2024. Program actions include headcount reductions from terminations, not filing certain
open positions and facility closures.The expanded program charges are expected to be primarily cash expenditures
related to severance and asset disposals.
